package selfProgramming;

public class Boolean {

	public static void main(String[] args) {
		// TODO Auto-generated method stub
		boolean x=true;
		boolean y=false;
		
		System.out.println("Is the following statement " +x+ " or " +y+ "?");
		System.out.println("\nThe world is round\t" +x);
		System.out.println("Spider has 10 legs\t" +y);
		System.out.println("6 is an odd number\t" +y);
    
Output

Is the following statement true or false?

The world is round	true
Spider has 10 legs	false
6 is an odd number	false
